OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain becoming widespread
OL,7,Fthis evening, likely merging into more
OL,8,Fpersistent and occasionally heavy rain
OL,9,Fovernight. Rain only erratically
OL,10,Fclearing east after dawn, but still
OL,11,Fsome locally heavy showers following.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FEarly cloud will break with
OL,14,Fsome bright or sunny spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping, but also scattered
OL,16,Fshowers. These turning heavy in
OL,17,Fplaces, with thunder and hail
OL,18,Fpossible, especially during the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
