OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain spreading east on
OL,7,FWednesday, isolated blustery showers
OL,8,Ffollowing. Sunny spells, scattered
OL,9,Fblustery showers Thursday, perhaps
OL,10,Fheavy and thundery. Drier Friday, but
OL,11,Ffurther showers possible. Feeling
OL,12,Frather cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
